, pero necesitamos ayuda para conseguirlo. ¡Si aún [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class=\"rss-widget\"><ul><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://ma.tt/2015/12/george-lakoff/\'>Matt: George Lakoff</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wptavern.com/joost-de-valk-on-the-lessons-learned-after-releasing-wordpress-seo-3-0\'>WPTavern: Joost de Valk on the Lessons Learned After Releasing WordPress SEO 3.0</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wptavern.com/freemius-insights-enables-plugin-developers-to-make-data-driven-decisions\'>WPTavern: Freemius Insights Enables Plugin Developers to Make Data-Driven Decisions</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"rss-widget\"><ul><li class=\'dashboard-news-plugin\'><span>Plugin popular:</span> <a href=\'https://wordpress.org/plugins/updraftplus/\' class=\'dashboard-news-plugin-link\'>UpdraftPlus Backup and Restoration</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=\'plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=updraftplus&amp;_wpnonce=cdeeb78474&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800\' class=\'thickbox\' title=\'UpdraftPlus Backup and Restoration\'>Instalar</a>)</span></li></ul></div>','no'),(1296,'_site_transient_timeout_theme_roots','1449175366','yes'),(1297,'_site_transient_theme_roots','a:1:{s:9:\"singluten\";s:7:\"/themes\";}','yes'),(1298,'_site_transient_update_plugins','O:8:\"stdClass\":4:{s:12:\"last_checked\";i:1449173571;s:8:\"response\";a:1:{s:45:\"tiny-compress-images/tiny-compress-images.php\";O:8:\"stdClass\":6:{s:2:\"id\";s:5:\"57677\";s:4:\"slug\";s:20:\"tiny-compress-images\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:45:\"tiny-compress-images/tiny-compress-images.php\";s:11:\"new_version\";s:5:\"1.5.0\";s:3:\"url\";s:51:\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tiny-compress-images/\";s:7:\"package\";s:69:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/tiny-compress-images.1.5.0.zip\";}}s:12:\"translations\";a:0:{}s:9:\"no_update\";a:4:{s:30:\"advanced-custom-fields/acf.php\";O:8:\"stdClass\":6:{s:2:\"id\";s:5:\"21367\";s:4:\"slug\";s:22:\"ad